{
  "source": {
    "project": "Sakura PACS",
    "notes": [
      "Chi dinh PACS dung OMI_O23 de gui thong tin nguoi benh, ho so va dich vu CDHA/TDCN sang PACS.",
      "Cap nhat trang thai dung OMI_O23/OML_O21 de tra trang thai tiep nhan, thuc hien hoac huy ve HIS.",
      "Tra ket qua dung ORU_R01 de gui mo ta, ket luan, phieu ket qua, link anh va canh bao ve HIS.",
      "Mot so truong phu thuoc thiet lap chung nhu tien to ma nguoi benh, gio sinh, so dien thoai, MSH-3/MSH-4."
    ]
  },
